lead_paragraph: Angelique Kerber lost for the first time since becoming the No. 1-ranked player, losing to Petra Kvitova in the third round of the Wuhan Open on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Top-Ranked Kerber Falls to Kvitova at Wuhan Open
